quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  19,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  19,1,"kaaf, hay, y, a, s"
  19,2,zikar hai uss rehmat ka jo tairay rab ne apne bande Zikria par ki thi
  19,3,jabkay uss ne apne rab ko chupkay chupkay puraka
  19,4,"uss ne arz kya"" ae parvar-digaar, meri haddiyan taq ghul gayi hain aur sir burhapay se bharak utha hai ae parvar-digaar, mein kabhi tujh se dua maang kar namuraad nahi raha"
  19,5,"mujhe apne peechay apne bhai bundon ki buraiyon ka khauf hai, aur meri biwi banjh hai to mujhe apne fzlِ khaas se aik waris ataa kar day"
  19,6,"jo mera waris bhi ho aur aalِ Yaqoob ki meeras bhi paye, aur ae parvar-digaar, uss ko aik pasandeeda ensaan bana """
  19,7,"( jawab diya gaya )"" ae Zikria, hum tujhe aik larke ki basharat dete hain jis ka naam yahya ho ga hum ne iss naam ka koi aadmi is se pehlay peda nahi kya """
  19,8,"arz kya,"" parvar-digaar, bhala mere haan kaisay beta hoga jabkay meri biwi banjh hai aur mein boorha ho kar sookh chuka hon? """
  19,9,"jawab mila"" aisa hi ho ga tera rab farmata hai ke yeh to mere liye aik zara si baat hai, aakhir is se pehlay mein tujhe peda kar chuka hon jab ke to koi cheez nah tha """
  19,10,"Zikria ne kaha,"" parvar-digaar, mere liye koi nishani muqarrar kar day"" farmaya"" tairay liye nishani yeh hai ke to pihm teen din logon se baat nah kar sakay """
  19,11,chunancha woh maharab se nikal kar apni qoum ke samnay aaya aur is ne isharay se un ko hadaayat ki ke subah o shaam tasbeeh karo
  19,12,""" ae yahya! kitaab Ellahi ko mazboot thaam le"" hum ne ussay bachpan hi mein"" hukum"" se nawaza"
  19,13,aur apni taraf se is ko naram dili aur pakizgee ataa ki aur woh bara parhaizgaar
  19,14,aur apne walidain ka haq shanaas tha woh jabbar nah tha aur nah nafarman
  19,15,salam uss par jis roz ke woh peda howa aur jis din woh marey aur jis roz woh zindah kar ke uthaya jaye
  19,16,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, is kitaab mein maryam ka haal bayan karo, jabkay woh apne logon se allag ho kar Sharqi janib gosha nasheen ho gayi thi"
  19,17,aur parda daal kar unn se choup baithi thi is haalat mein hum ne is ke paas apni rooh ko ( yani farishtay ko ) bheja aur woh is ke samnay aik poooray ensaan ki shakal mein namodaar ho gaya
  19,18,"maryam yakayak bol uthi ke"" agar to koi khuda taras aadmi hai to mein tujh se rehman ki panah maangti hon """
  19,19,"uss ne kaha"" mein to tairay rab ka Farstada hon aur is liye bheja gaya hon ke tujhe aik pakeeza larka dun """
  19,20,"maryam ne kaha"" mere haan kaisay larka hoga jabkay mujhe kisi bashar ne chuva taq nahi hai aur mein koi badkaar aurat nahi hon """
  19,21,"farishtay ne kaha"" aisa hi hoga, tera rab farmata hai ke aisa karna mere liye bohat aasaan hai aur hum yeh is liye karen ge ke uss larke ko logon ke liye aik nishani banayen aur apni taraf se aik rehmat aur yeh kaam ho kar rehna hai """
  19,22,maryam ko is bachay ka hamal reh gaya aur woh is hamal ko liye hue aik door ke maqam par chali gayi
  19,23,"phir zichgi ki takleef ne ussay aik khajoor ke darakht ke neechay pouncha diya woh kehnay lagi"" kash mein is se pehlay hi mar jati aur mera naam o nishaan nah rehta """
  19,24,"farishtay ne painti se is ko pukaar kar kaha"" gham ne kar tairay rab ne tairay neechay aik chashma rawan kar diya hai"
  19,25,"aur to zara iss darakht ke tanay ko hila, tairay oopar tar o taaza khjorin tapak parrin gi"
  19,26,"pas to kha aur pi aur apni ankhen thandhi kar phir agar koi aadmi tujhe nazar aeye to is se keh day ke mein ne Rehman ke liye rozay ki Nazar maani hai, is liye aaj mein kisi se nah bolon gi """
  19,27,"phir woh is bachay ko liye hue apni qoum mein aayi log kehnay lagey"" ae maryam, yeh to too ne bara paap kar dala"
  19,28,"ae Haroon ki behan, nah tera baap koi bura aadmi tha aur nah teri maa hi koi badkaar aurat thi """
  19,29,"maryam ne bachay ki taraf ishara kar diya logon ne kaha"" hum iss se kya baat karen jo gehware mein para howa aik bacha hai? """
  19,30,"bacha bol utha"" mein Allah ka bandah hon uss ne mujhe kitaab di, aur nabi banaya"
  19,31,"aur babarkat kya jahan bhi mein rahon, aur namaz aur zkoh ki pabandi ka hukum diya jab taq mein zindah rahon"
  19,32,"aur apni walida ka haq ada karne wala banaya, aur mujh ko jabbar aur shaqqi nahi banaya"
  19,33,"salam hai mujh par jabkay mein peda howa aur jabkay mein mron aur jabkay zindah kar ke uthaya jaoon """
  19,34,yeh hai eesa Ibn maryam aur yeh hai uss ke baray mein woh sachhi baat jis mein log shak kar rahay hain
  19,35,"Allah ka yeh kaam nahi hai ke woh kisi ko beta banaye woh pak zaat hai woh jab kisi baat ka faisla karta hai to kehta hai ke ho ja, aur bas woh ho jati hai"
  19,36,"( aur eesa ne kaha tha ke )"" Allah mera rab bhi hai aur tumhara rab bhi, pas tum usi ki bandagi karo, yahi seedhi raah hai """
  19,37,magar phir mukhtalif giroh baahum ikhtilaaf karne lagey so jin logon ne kufar kya un ke liye woh waqt barri tabahi ka hoga
  19,38,"jab ke woh aik bara din dekhen ge jab woh hamaray samnay haazir hon ge uss roz to unn ke kaan bhi khoob sun rahay hon ge aur unn ki ankhen bhi khoob dekhatii hon gi, magar aaj yeh zalim khuli gumraahi mein mubtala hain"
  19,39,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, iss haalat mein jabkay yeh log ghaafil hain aur imaan nahi laa rahay hain, aِnhin is din se dara do jabkay faisla kar diya jaye ga aur pachtaway ke siwa koi charah car nah hoga"
  19,40,aakhir kaar hum hi zameen aur is ki saari cheezon ke waris hon ge aur sab hamari taraf hipalta-ay jayen ge
  19,41,"aur is kitaab mein ibrahim ka qissa bayan karo, be shak woh aik raast baz ensaan aur aik nabi tha"
  19,42,"( inhen zara uss mauqa ki yaad dlao ) jabkay uss ne apne baap se kaha ke"" abba jaan, aap kyun unn cheezon ki ibadat karte hain jo nah sunthee hain nah dekhatii hain aur nah aap ka koi kaam bana sakti hain ?"
  19,43,"abba jaan, mere paas aik aisa ilm aaya hai jo aap ke paas nahi aaya, aap mere peechay chalein, mein aap ko seedha rasta batau ga"
  19,44,"abba jaan! aap shetan ki bandagi nah karen, shetan to rehman ka nafarman hai"
  19,45,"abba jaan, mujhe dar hai ke kahin aap Rehman ke azaab mein mubtala nah ho jayen aur shetan ke saathi ban kar rahen """
  19,46,"baap ne kaha"" ibrahim, kya to mere mabodon se phir gaya hai? agar to baz nah aaya to mein tujhe sangsar kar dun ga bas to hamesha ke liye mujh se allag ho ja """
  19,47,"ibrahim ne kaha"" salam hai aap ko mein apne rab se dua karoon ga ke aap ko maaf kar day, mera rab mujh par bara hi meharban hai"
  19,48,"mein aap logon ko bhi chhorta hon aur unn hstyon ko bhi jinhein aap log khuda ko chore kar puraka karte hain mein to apne rab hi ko poukaron ga, umeed hai ke mein apne rab ko pukaar ke namuraad nah rahon ga """
  19,49,pas jab woh unn logon se aur unn ke مma'bodane ghair Allah se juda ho gaya to hum ne uss ko ishaq aur yaqoob jaisi aulaad di aur har aik ko nabi banaya
  19,50,aur un ko apni rehmat se nawaza aur un ko sachhi namwari ataa ki
  19,51,aur zikar karo is kitaab mein moose ka woh aik cheeda shakhs tha aur rasool nabi tha
  19,52,hum ne uss ko tor ke dahni janib se puraka aur raaz ki guftagu se is ko taqarab ataa kya
  19,53,aur apni meharbani se is ke bhai haroon ko nabi bana kar ussay ( madad gaar ke tor par ) diya
  19,54,aur is kitaab mein Ismael ka zikar karo woh waday ka sacha tha aur rasool nabi tha
  19,55,woh apne ghar walon ko namaz aur zkoh ka hukum deta tha aur apne rab ke nazdeek aik pasandeeda ensaan tha
  19,56,aur is kitaab mein Adrees ka zikar karo woh aikrasbaaz ensaan aur aik nabi tha
  19,57,aur usay hum ne buland maqam par uthaya tha
  19,58,"yeh woh paighambar hain jin par Allah ne inaam farmaya aadam ki aulaad mein se, aur unn logon ki nasal se jinhein hum ne Nooh ke sath kashti par sawaar kya tha, a war ibrahim ki nasal se aur Israel ki nasal se aur yeh un logon mein se thay jin ko hum ne hadaayat bakhsh aur bargzida kya un ka haal yeh tha ke jab Rehman ki ayaat un ko sunai jatein to rotay hue sjday mein gir jatay thay"
  19,59,"phir un ke baad woh nakhlf log un ke janasheen hue jinhon ne namaz ko zaya kya aur khwahisaat nafs ki pairwi ki, pas qareeb hai ke woh gumraahi ke injaam se dochar hon"
  19,60,Albata jo tauba kar len aur imaan le ayen aur naik amli ikhtiyar kar len woh jannat mein daakhil hon ge aur un ki zarraa barabar haq talfi nah ho gi
  19,61,un ke liye hamesha rehne wali jannaten hain jin ka Rehman ne apne bundon se Dur parda wada kar rakha hai aur yaqeenan yeh wada poora ho kar rehna hai
  19,62,"wahan woh koi be Hooda baat nah sُnin ge, jo kuch bhi sُnin ge theek hi sunen ge aur un ka rizaq inhen pihm subah o shaam milta rahay ga"
  19,63,yeh hai woh jannat jis ka waris hum apne bundon mein se uss ko banayen ge jo parhaizgaar raha hai
  19,64,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum tumahray rab ke hukum ke baghair nahi utra karte jo kuch hamaray agay hai aur jo kuch peechay hai aur jo kuch is ke darmain hai har cheez ka maalik wohi hai aur tumhara rab bhoolnay wala nahi hai"
  19,65,woh rab hai asmano ka aur zameen ka aur unn saari cheezon ka jo aasman o zameen ke darmain hain pas tum uss ke bandagi karo aur usi ki bandagi par saabit qadam raho kya hai koi hasti tumahray ilm mein is ki hum paya ?
  19,66,ensaan kehta hai kya waqai jab mein mar chukun ga to phir zindah kar ke nikaal laya jaoon ga ?
  19,67,kya ensaan ko yaad nahi aata ke hum pehlay is ko peda kar chuke hain jabkay woh kuch bhi nah tha ?
  19,68,"tairay Rab ki qasam, hum zaroor un sab ko aur un ke sath shyatin ko bhi ghair layein ge, phir jahannum ke gird laa kar inhen ghutnon ke bil gira den ge"
  19,69,phir har giroh mein se har uss shakhs ko chhant len ge jo Rehman ke muqablay mein ziyada sarkash bana howa tha
  19,70,phir yeh hum jantay hain ke un mein se kon sab se barh kar jahannum mein jhonkay jaane ka mustahiq hai
  19,71,"tum mein se koi aisa nahi hai jo jahannum par warid nah ho, yeh to aik tey shuda baat hai jisay poora karna tairay rab ka zimma hai"
  19,72,phir hum unn logon ko bacha len ge jo ( duniya mein ) mut-taqi thay aur zaalmon ko usi mein gira howa chore den ge
  19,73,"inn logon ko jab hamari khُli khُli ayaat sunai jati hain to inkaar karne walay imaan laane walon se kehte hain"" batao hum dono garohoon mein se kon behtar haalat mein hai aur kis ki mujlisain ziyada shandaar hain? """
  19,74,halaank un se pehlay hum kitni hi aisi qomon ko halaak kar chuke hain jo inn se ziyada sir o samaan rakhti theen aur zahiri shaan o Shaukat mein inn se barhi hui theen
  19,75,"inn se kaho, jo shakhs gumraahi mein mubtala hota hai ussay Rehman dheel diya karta hai yahan taq ke jab aisay log woh cheez dekh letay hain jis ka unn se wada kya gaya hai khuwa woh azaab Ellahi ho ya qayamat ki gharri tab inhen maloom ho jata hai ke kis ka haal kharab hai aur kis ka jatha kamzor !"
  19,76,is ke bar aks jo log raah e raast ikhtiyar karte hain Allah un ko raast rawi mein taraqqi ataa farmata hai aur baqi reh jaane wali naikian hi tairay rab ke nazdeek jaza aur injaam ke aitbaar se behtar hain
  19,77,phir to ne dekha uss shakhs ko jo hamari ayaat ko maan-ne se inkaar karta hai aur kehta hai ke mein to maal aur aulaad se nawaza hi jata rahon ga ?
  19,78,kya usay ghaib ka pata chal gaya hai ya is ne Rehman se koi ehad le rakha hai ?
  19,79,"hargiz nahi, jo kuch yeh bikta hai usay hum likh len ge aur is ke liye saza mein aur ziyada izafah karen ge"
  19,80,jis sir o samaan aur lao lashkar ka yeh zikar kar raha hai woh sab hamaray paas reh jaye ga aur yeh akela hamaray samnay haazir hoga
  19,81,inn logon ne Allah ko chore kar apne kuch khuda bana rakhay hain taakay woh inn ke pshtiban hon
  19,82,koi pshtiban nah hoga woh sab un ki ibadat ka inkaar karen ge aur ultay inn ke mukhalif ban jayen ge
  19,83,kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke hum ne inn munkareen haq par shyatin chore rakhay hain jo aِnhin khob khob ( Mukhalfat haq par ) aksa rahay hain ?
  19,84,"acha, to ab inn par nuzool azaab ke liye betaab nah ho hum inn ke din gun rahay hain"
  19,85,woh din anay wala hai jab mut-taqi logon ko hum mehmanon ki terhan Rehman ke huzoor paish karen ge
  19,86,aur mujrimon ko pyase janwaron ki terhan jahannum ki taraf haank le jayen ge
  19,87,uss waqt log koi sifarish laane par Qadir nah hon ge bajuz uss ke jis ne Rehman ke huzoor se parwana haasil kar liya ho
  19,88,woh kehte hain ke Rehman ne kisi ko beta banaya hai
  19,89,sakht behooda baat hai jo tum log ghurr laaye ho
  19,90,"qareeb hai ke aasman phatt parrin, zameen shaqq ho jaye aur pahar gir jayen"
  19,91,is baat par ke logon ne Rehman ke liye aulaad honay ka daawa kya !
  19,92,Rehman ki yeh shaan nahi hai ke woh kisi ko beta banaye
  19,93,zameen aur aasman ke andar jo bhi hain sab is ke huzoor bundon ki hesiyat se paish honay walay hain
  19,94,sab par woh muheet hai aur is ne unn ko shumaar kar rakha hai
  19,95,sab qayamat ke roz fardan fardan is ke samnay haazir hon ge
  19,96,yaqeenan jo log imaan le aeye hain aur amal Saleh kar rahay hain anqareeb Rehman unn ke liye dilon mein mohabbat peda kar day ga
  19,97,"pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, iss kalaam ko hum ne aasaan kar ke tumhari zabaan mein isi liye nazil kya hai ke tum parhaiz gaaron ko khushkhabri day do aur hatt dharm logon ko dara do"
  19,98,"un se pehlay hum kitni hi qomon ko halaak kar chuke hain, phir aaj kahin tum un ka nishaan paate ho ya unn ki bhanak bhi kahin sunai deti hai ?"
